OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining showers will fade away,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry evening with
OL,8,Flight winds. Cloud will increase from
OL,9,Fthe west later, bringing a few
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain before dawn. Winds
OL,11,Ffreshening later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy, with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain slowly moving north-
OL,15,Feastwards through the morning. Some
OL,16,Fbrighter intervals developing into the
OL,17,Fafternoon and evening, but with a few
OL,18,Fheavy showers. Brisk coastal winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
