OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy on Sunday, some rain
OL,7,Fover hills. Early rain clearing east
OL,8,FMonday, sunny spells, scattered
OL,9,Fshowers following. Cooler and showery
OL,10,FTuesday. Showers occasionally heavy,
OL,11,Fperhaps thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
